&lt;h2&gt;Why use Cloud.net?&lt;/h2&gt;  
Cloud.net is a marketplace of Clouds and VPS servers, with worldwide locations and more being added constantly.

You get no single provider lock-in or penalty to change providers, a unified invoice, full transparency on how each cloud performs with our Cloud Index Score, price comparison, ability to deploy to many different regions and providers and manage it all from a single interface.  

&lt;h2&gt;Free DNS hosting&lt;/h2&gt;  
With any account, we offer completely free DNS hosting, using anycast DNS from 13 worldwide locations. See all the details at https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/sections/201359850-DNS

&lt;h2&gt;Full API&lt;/h2&gt;  
Automate your deployment and management - we have a full API backend that allows you to create, and manage your servers using any tool you like. See the docs at https://api.cloud.net/docs.  

&lt;h2&gt;One click app deployment&lt;/h2&gt;  
Using our application deployment service to install more than 21 applications - see them all at https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/articles/207358950-What-applications-are-available-

&lt;h2&gt;Earn more - suggest a feature, or find a bug, and get credits!&lt;/h2&gt;
This is just for Lowendtalk users, but using our &lt;a href="https://help.cloud.net/hc/en-us/community/topics/200026301-Feature-Requests"&gt;new feature suggestion box&lt;/a&gt;, if you suggest a new feature, I'll give you a $10 credit. Find a bug? Just let me know at t@cloud.net, and I'll get you credited for $20. We're serious about improving!  

&lt;h2&gt;The billing details...&lt;/h2&gt;
Don't look so glum - we've made it easy. &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;$10 deposits are now available at Cloud.net.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. We accept Paypal &amp; credit card - everything is PAYG, and we bill for a total of 672 total hours per month. If you cancel a server before the end of the month, you're credited back for the unused time. Here's what's hot - &lt;strong&gt;coupon codes apply to your entire account, so you could create 100 servers, and pay just $38 in the first month.&lt;/strong&gt;
